                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210214-40-defend510 t18210214-40-punish262"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>. Aged 45.</p>
               <p>PARSONS - <rs id="t18210214-40-verdict263" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18210214-40-verdict263" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18210214-40-verdict263" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. - <rs id="t18210214-40-punish264" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18210214-40-punish264" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210214-40-defend508 t18210214-40-punish264"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>. Aged 38.</p>
               <p>Parsons Recommended to Mercy.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Best.</p>
